<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Atlas 市场风险监控 · {{ date }}</title>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0f131a">
<link rel="manifest" href="manifest.webmanifest">
<link rel="icon" href="favicon-32.png" sizes="32x32">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="apple-touch-icon.png">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Atlas">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f4f6f9;
    --panel: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1a1f28;
    --muted: #5c6673;
    --line: #e2e7ee;
    --good: #2e9658;
    --good-bg: #e5f5ec;
    --warn: #c98a12;
    --warn-bg: #fbf1d8;
    --bad: #cf3b3b;
    --bad-bg: #fbe6e6;
    --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(20,30,50,.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(20,30,50,.06);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root {
      --bg: #0f131a;
      --panel: #171d27;
      --ink: #e7ecf3;
      --muted: #9aa5b3;
      --line: #262e3a;
      --good: #4fd08a;
      --good-bg: #16301f;
      --warn: #e7b74a;
      --warn-bg: #322a11;
      --bad: #f27272;
      --bad-bg: #341717;
      --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC",
      "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .wrap { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 16px 64px; }
  h1 { font-size: 20px; margin: 0; }
  h2 {
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: .04em; color: var(--muted);
    margin: 32px 0 12px; text-transform: none; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .sub { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
  header.top {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .metrics { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; }
  .metrics b { color: var(--ink); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

  /* ---- regime light ---- */
  .regime {
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 22px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border: 1px solid var(--line); display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: center;
  }
  .regime .dot { font-size: 46px; line-height: 1; }
  .regime .body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .regime .name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
  .regime .reason { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .regime .stance { margin-top: 6px; font-size: 14px; }
  .regime-on { background: var(--good-bg); border-color: var(--good); }
  .regime-caution { background: var(--warn-bg); border-color: var(--warn); }
  .regime-off { background: var(--bad-bg); border-color: var(--bad); }
  .regime-oversold { background: var(--warn-bg); border-color: #d98a2b; }
  .change-badge {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---- tags ---- */
  .tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tag-good { color: var(--good); background: var(--good-bg); }
  .tag-warn { color: var(--warn); background: var(--warn-bg); }
  .tag-bad  { color: var(--bad);  background: var(--bad-bg); }

  /* ---- market cards ---- */
  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
  .card {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .card .head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .card .nm { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
  .card .tk { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .card .scores { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin: 10px 0 6px; }
  .card .scores .lab { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }
  .card .scores .val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .card .dist { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .card .dist b { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .card .price { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 2px 0 4px; }
  .card .price b { color: var(--ink); font-size: 17px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .heat .cell .px { font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; margin: 1px 0 3px; opacity: .95; }
  .pos { color: var(--good); } .neg { color: var(--bad); }

  /* ---- sector heatmap ---- */
  .heat { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; }
  .heat .cell {
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
  }
  .heat .cell .nm { font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
  .heat .cell .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 12px; }
  .heat .cell .t { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-weight: 700; }
  .heat .cell .tag { background: rgba(255,255,255,.75); }

  /* ---- multi-asset bar ---- */
  .assets { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
  .asset {
    background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px;
  }
  .asset .nm { font-weight: 600; }
  .asset .tk { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; }
  .asset .arrow { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }

  /* ---- stock table ---- */
  .tablewrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--line); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: var(--panel); font-size: 14px; }
  th, td { padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); white-space: nowrap; }
  th { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; background: var(--panel); }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  td.num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  tbody tr.tone-good { background: rgba(46,150,88,.06); }
  tbody tr.tone-warn { background: rgba(201,138,18,.07); }
  tbody tr.tone-bad  { background: rgba(207,59,59,.07); }
  tbody tr.tone-good td:first-child { box-shadow: inset 3px 0 var(--good); }
  tbody tr.tone-warn td:first-child { box-shadow: inset 3px 0 var(--warn); }
  tbody tr.tone-bad  td:first-child { box-shadow: inset 3px 0 var(--bad); }
  a.tklink { color: var(--ink); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--muted); }
  a.tklink:hover { color: var(--good); border-color: var(--good); }
  .hintlist { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
  .hint { padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
  .hint.risk { color: var(--bad); background: var(--bad-bg); }
  .hint.opp { color: var(--good); background: var(--good-bg); }
  .dash { color: var(--muted); }

  /* ---- alerts ---- */
  .alerts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .alert {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--panel);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow); border-left-width: 4px;
  }
  .alert.risk { border-left-color: var(--bad); }
  .alert.opp  { border-left-color: var(--good); }
  .alert .ic { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .alert .title { font-weight: 700; }
  .alert .title .kind { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 999px; margin-left: 6px; }
  .alert.risk .kind { color: var(--bad); background: var(--bad-bg); }
  .alert.opp .kind { color: var(--good); background: var(--good-bg); }
  .alert .detail { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .alert .who { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .empty { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 2px; }
  footer { margin-top: 40px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .wrap { padding: 14px 10px 48px; }
    h1 { font-size: 20px; }
    .regime .dot { font-size: 40px; }
    .kpi .val, .card .scores .val { font-size: 18px; }
    table { font-size: 13px; }
    th, td { padding: 6px 8px; }
    .cards, .heat, .assets { gap: 8px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap">
  <header class="top">
    <div>
      <h1>Atlas · 市场风险与机会监控</h1>
      <div class="sub">截至 {{ date }} 收盘　·　数据 {{ source }}{% if prev_date %}　·　对比 {{ prev_date }}{% endif %}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metrics">
      广度 <b>{{ breadth_pct }}</b>　·　VIX <b>{{ vix }}</b>
    </div>
  </header>

  {# ---------- 1) 市场制度灯 ---------- #}
  <section class="regime {{ regime.cls }}">
    <div class="dot">{{ regime.light }}</div>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="name">{{ regime.label }}</div>
      <div class="reason">{{ regime.reason }}</div>
      <div class="stance">应对：{{ regime.stance }}</div>
      {% if regime.changed and regime.prev %}
      <div class="change-badge">较昨日变化：{{ regime.prev.light }} {{ regime.prev.label }} → {{ regime.light }} {{ regime.label }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {# ---------- 2) 大盘卡片区 ---------- #}
  <h2>大盘</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for m in markets %}
    <div class="card">
      <div class="head">
        <div><span class="nm">{{ m.name }}</span> <span class="tk">{{ m.ticker }}</span></div>
        <span class="tag {{ m.status.cls }}">{{ m.status.icon }} {{ m.status.label }}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price">现价 <b>{{ m.price }}</b> <span class="{{ 'pos' if m.chg_good else 'neg' }}">{{ m.chg }}</span></div>
      <div class="scores">
        <div><div class="lab">趋势 T</div><div class="val">{{ m.T }}</div></div>
        <div><div class="lab">风险 R</div><div class="val">{{ m.R }}</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dist">距200线 <b class="{{ 'pos' if m.dist200_good else 'neg' }}">{{ m.dist200 }}</b></div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {# ---------- 3) 行业热力图 ---------- #}
  <h2>行业热力图（按趋势分排序，绿=强 红=弱）</h2>
  <div class="heat">
    {% for s in sectors %}
    <div class="cell" style="{{ s.style }}">
      <div class="nm">{{ s.name }}</div>
      <div class="px">现价 {{ s.price }}　{{ s.chg }}</div>
      <div class="row">
        <span class="tk">{{ s.ticker }}</span>
        <span class="t">T {{ s.T }}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="tag {{ s.status.cls }}">{{ s.status.icon }} {{ s.status.label }}</span>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {# ---------- 4) 多资产条 ---------- #}
  <h2>多资产（风险偏好晴雨表）</h2>
  <div class="assets">
    {% for a in multi_assets %}
    <div class="asset">
      <div>
        <div class="nm">{{ a.name }}</div>
        <div class="tk">{{ a.ticker }}　现价 {{ a.price }} <span class="{{ 'pos' if a.chg_good else 'neg' }}">{{ a.chg }}</span>　T {{ a.T }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="arrow tag {{ a.arrow.cls }}" title="{{ a.arrow.label }}">{{ a.arrow.icon }} {{ a.arrow.label }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {# ---------- 5) 自选个股表 ---------- #}
  <h2>自选个股</h2>
  {% if stocks %}
  <div class="tablewrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>个股</th><th>现价</th><th>当日</th><th>趋势状态</th><th>动量(12-1)</th><th>距52周高</th><th>风险旗标</th><th>当日提示</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for s in stocks %}
        <tr class="tone-{{ s.tone }}">
          <td><b>{% if s.link %}<a class="tklink" href="{{ s.link }}">{{ s.name }} ›</a>{% else %}{{ s.name }}{% endif %}</b> <span class="tk" style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px">{{ s.ticker }}</span></td>
          <td class="num"><b>{{ s.price }}</b></td>
          <td class="num {{ 'pos' if s.chg_good else 'neg' }}">{{ s.chg }}</td>
          <td><span class="tag {{ s.trend.cls }}">{{ s.trend.icon }} {{ s.trend.label }}</span></td>
          <td class="num {{ 'pos' if s.mom_good else 'neg' }}">{{ s.mom }}</td>
          <td class="num">{{ s.dist_high }}</td>
          <td><span class="tag {{ s.risk.cls }}">{{ s.risk.icon }} {{ s.risk.label }}</span></td>
          <td>
            {% if s.hints %}
            <div class="hintlist">
              {% for h in s.hints %}
              <span class="hint {{ 'risk' if h.is_risk else 'opp' }}">{{ '⚠️' if h.is_risk else '✨' }} {{ h.title }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% else %}<span class="dash">—</span>{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <div class="empty">未配置自选个股。</div>
  {% endif %}

  {# ---------- 6) 今日提示区 ---------- #}
  <h2>今日提示（按重要性排序）</h2>
  {% if alerts %}
  <div class="alerts">
    {% for a in alerts %}
    <div class="alert {{ 'risk' if a.is_risk else 'opp' }}">
      <div class="ic">{{ a.icon }}</div>
      <div>
        <div class="title">{{ a.title }}<span class="kind">{{ a.kind_label }}</span></div>
        <div class="detail">{{ a.detail }}</div>
        <div class="who">{{ a.name }} · {{ a.ticker }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <div class="empty">今日无风险 / 机会提示。</div>
  {% endif %}

  <footer>
    数据来源 {{ source }}｜行情截至 {{ date }} 收盘｜报告生成于 {{ generated_at }}。<br>
    本仪表盘读的是市场情绪与风险状态，不预测顶底、不构成买卖建议。规则详见 architecture.md。<br>
    <a href="backtest.html" style="color:var(--good)">📊 生存回测报告</a>：系统在 2000/2008/2020/2022 大跌中是否及时转防御。
  </footer>
</div>

<script>
  if ('serviceWorker' in navigator) {
    addEventListener('load', function () {
      navigator.serviceWorker.register('sw.js').catch(function () {});
    });
  }
</script>
</body>
</html>
